{"id":11,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":11,"title":"D&C 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 7"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given to Joseph Smith the Prophet and Oliver Cowdery, at Harmony, Pennsylvania, April 1829, when they inquired through the Urim and Thummim as to whether John, the beloved disciple, tarried in the flesh or had died. The revelation is a translated version of the record made on parchment by John and hidden up by himself."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.1-3"},"1–3"],", John the Beloved will live until the Lord comes;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.4-8"},"4–8"],", Peter, James, and John hold gospel keys."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.1","order":"06.05.007.1183"},["b","1"],"And the Lord said unto me:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"John"],", my beloved, what",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"desirest"],"thou? For if you shall ask what you will, it shall be granted unto you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.2","order":"06.05.007.1184"},["b","2"],"And I said unto him: Lord, give unto me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"power"],"over",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"death"],", that I may live and bring souls unto thee."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.3","order":"06.05.007.1185"},["b","3"],"And the Lord said unto me: Verily, verily, I say unto thee, because thou desirest this thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tarry"],"until I come in my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"glory"],", and shalt",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"prophesy"],"before nations, kindreds, tongues and people."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.4","order":"06.05.007.1186"},["b","4"],"And for this cause the Lord said unto Peter: If I will that he tarry till I come, what is that to thee? For he desired of me that he might bring",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"souls"],"unto me, but thou desiredst that thou mightest speedily come unto me in my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"kingdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.5","order":"06.05.007.1187"},["b","5"],"I say unto thee, Peter, this was a good desire; but my beloved has desired that he might do more, or a greater",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"work"],"yet among men than what he has before done."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.6","order":"06.05.007.1188"},["b","6"],"Yea, he has undertaken a greater work; therefore I will make him as flaming fire and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"ministering"],"angel; he shall minister for those who shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"heirs"],"of salvation who dwell on the earth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.7","order":"06.05.007.1189"},["b","7"],"And I will make thee to minister for him and for thy brother James; and unto you three I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"give"],"this power and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"keys"],"of this ministry until I come."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.8","order":"06.05.007.1190"},["b","8"],"Verily I say unto you, ye shall both have according to your desires, for ye both",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"joy"],"in that which ye have desired."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.1a","order":"06.05.007.1191"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.26.26-27"},"John 19:26 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/20.2.2-9"},"20:2 (2–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.1b","order":"06.05.007.1193"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/1.7.7-12"},"2 Chr. 1:7 (7–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.1.1-12"},"3 Ne. 28:1 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.2a","order":"06.05.007.1195"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death-power-over"},"TG Death, Power over"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.2b","order":"06.05.007.1197"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.27"},"Luke 9:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.3a","order":"06.05.007.1199"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/21.22.20-25"},"John 21:22 (20–25)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/translated-beings"},"TG Translated Beings"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.3b","order":"06.05.007.1201"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/glory"},"TG Glory"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"},"Jesus Christ, Glory of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.3c","order":"06.05.007.1203"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/10.11"},"Rev. 10:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.4a","order":"06.05.007.1205"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worth-of-souls"},"Worth of Souls"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.4b","order":"06.05.007.1207"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"},"TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.5a","order":"06.05.007.1209"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.24.23-24"},"Philip. 1:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.9.1-12"},"3 Ne. 28:9 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.6a","order":"06.05.007.1211"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/1.14"},"Heb. 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.25"},"D&C 43:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.5"},"130:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.6b","order":"06.05.007.1213"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.88"},"D&C 76:88"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.7a","order":"06.05.007.1215"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.19"},"Matt. 16:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.7b","order":"06.05.007.1217"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.7"},"Acts 15:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.28"},"D&C 6:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.72"},"JS—H 1:72"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.8a","order":"06.05.007.1219"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."]]}
